    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paper or cardboard covers that form illustrated slip-cases for records, such as a seven-inch 45 rpm phonograph record, or slim  books, to protect and to advertise the contents of the book or record.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
